  <summary date="2015-03-26T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Save Access to a Valuable Investment Needed to Generate Savings Act of 2015 or the SAVINGS Act 

Directs the Department of the Treasury to: (1) allow individual taxpayers an option to purchase U.S. savings bonds in paper form with a portion or all of a tax refund during the period ending on December 31, 2020; or (2) implement an alternative option that allows for the gifting of U.S. savings bonds, serves the unbanked, and retains the ability to sign-up on the return of tax.</summary>
